  tutorialLevelTexts:
  - Welcome to the derby!
  - Hold 'W' to accelerate
  - Hold 'S' or Space to break
  - Hold 'A' and 'D' to turn
  - Get air time, drift, and ram stuff!
  - Why?\n
  - To keep your viewers up
  - You don't wanna know what happens if you don't.
  buttonText: '*Click Tab to continue'
